1: January 20, Changchun, Jilin. China Railway 17th Bureau owed wages, and migrant workers gathered at the company to demand wages;
2: January 19, Henan. Workers jumped off the building to demand wages;
3: January 15, Xi'an, Shaanxi. Xi'an Construction Group owed wages, and workers lay at the door of the construction site to demand wages.
4: January 17, Guangdong. Zhongcheng Jinglong real estate project owed wages to construction workers, and workers demanded wages at the sales office.
